author: Second Wind
description:
Misc. A Tiny Tale is a new 3D platformer from Tinyware Games that would've fit perfectly alongside Chibi-Robo! and the rest of the Nintendo GameCube library.

Check out Misc. A Tiny Tale on Steam -- https://store.steampowered.com/app/1308940/Misc_A_Tiny_Tale/

If you dig our video essays, consider supporting us on Patreon! -- https://www.patreon.com/SecondWindGroup

title: Misc. A Tiny Tale Is the Best GameCube Game That Never Existed
